            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-amber-600 dark:group-hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors">Vercel Design</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-1">vercel.com/design</p>
